{"tid":2252841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男子涉何文田公眾地方行為不檢及未戴口罩被捕","createTime":"2020-10-21T17:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T01:49:27.000Z","uid":112747,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"329ade30ec1fc931716bb01188773496664d7621","tid":2252841,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:46:59.000Z","msg":"早幾日一男一女衝上巴士鬧人果單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名男子涉嫌在何文田干犯公眾地方行為不檢及在巴士上未有戴口罩被捕。<br />\n警方晚上在石硤尾邨，拘捕一名30歲男子。<br />\n案發在周二，一輛私家車停泊在何文田常盛街路邊，阻礙一輛巴士行駛。巴士司機要求私家車離開時，一男一女走上巴士並辱罵司機同乘客，造成混亂。<br />\n被捕男子涉嫌干犯公眾地方行為不檢及違反預防及控制疾病規例。他的私家車亦被警方扣查。"},{"pid":"249612efd1c4900b6d63445116a253f4cdfa96d8","tid":2252841,"uid":7452,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59074ce73b274459f3117ffd829cf9434a3f3ddf","tid":2252841,"uid":55637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"249612efd1c4900b6d63445116a253f4cdfa96d8","tid":2252841,"uid":7452,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:50:45.000Z","msg":"公屋真係出特別多mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聲大夾惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03da2d69f3cca139daa2fa9ac122bce37ab05e02","tid":2252841,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"271ab4f29a2bb96b6d2f657ee5e7577e68bab5b2","tid":2252841,"uid":7452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59074ce73b274459f3117ffd829cf9434a3f3ddf","tid":2252841,"uid":55637,"like":9